and Big Data Expo](https://www.ai-expo.net/europe/speaker/aslan-mehrabi/) on Wednesday in Amsterdam. He will cover how Smart Machine Bidding is the future of Machine-to-Machine payments and communication. MXC Ambassador G. will be joining him there on Thursday.\n\nNext week Jeff will be in China for the Nanjing Tech Week! He will also head over to Shanghai Yangpu District to meet with the government there and discuss the progress on the MXC rollout in Shanghai.\n\nThis has been this week’s news update. I look forward to speaking with all of you again next week. Until then, get active, get in the community, as us questions — because it’s only together that we can build the Future of IoT.","date":"June 17, 2019","metaDescription":"Aslan joined the LoRa Alliance annual event, and this week he will speak at the AI Data Expo in Amsterdam. Jeff will be in China for the Nanjing Tech Week.","video":"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZQ8zzlp1nsc","slug":"lorawan-sensor-roaming-and-the-ai-big-data-expo"},"tags":[],"author":{"author":"Jeff Stahlnecker","slug":"jeff-stahlnecker"},"zhch_post":{"post":{"slug":"lorawan传感器漫游和ai与大数据博览会"}},"zhtw_post":{"post":{"slug":"lorawan傳感器漫遊和ai與大數據博覽會"}},"ko_post":null},"hans":{"category":{"zhchCategory":"新闻更新","zhchSlug":"新闻更新"},"featuredImage":null,"title":"LoRaWAN传感器漫游和AI与大数据博览会","post":{"content":"## LoRaWAN传感器漫游和AI与大数据博览会\n\nAslan参加了LoRa联盟的年度活动， Aslan也将在阿姆斯特丹的AI数据博览会上发表演讲。 Jeff将在中国参加南京科技周，您有机会在那里见到他哟！\n\nMXC极域数据科学家Aslan Mehrabi加入了Lora联盟的技术和认证委员会， 在那里我们讨论了MXC极域如何解决LoRa迄今为止最大的问题：LoRAWAN漫游。感应器漫游以及如何构建即时合约。 当然，MXC极域协议和平行链可以很好地解决这些问题。\n\nAslan还将于周三在阿姆斯特丹的[AI大数据博览会](https://www.ai-expo.net/europe/speaker/aslan-mehrabi/)上发表演讲。 他将介绍智慧物联竞价如何解决合约问题。 周四MXC极域大使G.将加入他的行列。\n\n下周Jeff将要在中国参加南京科技周啦！ 他还将前往上海杨浦区与当地政府会面， 讨论MXC极域在上海推出的进展情况。\n\n这就是本周的新闻更新啦。 我很期待下周再跟你们聊聊。 在那之前，变得积极吧、加入我们的社群、问我们问题。因为只有我们在一起，我们才能建造物联网的未来。","date":"June 17, 2019","metaDescription":"Aslan参加了LoRa联盟的年度活动， Aslan也将在阿姆斯特丹的AI数据博览会上发表演讲。 Jeff将在中国参加南京科技周，您有机会在那里见到他哟！","video":"https://www.youtu